<!DOCTYPE html>


<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8"/>
<meta content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" name="viewport"/>
<title>Slide 19 - Recomendación</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@6.4.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link crossorigin="" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" rel="preconnect"/>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&amp;display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
<style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f3f4f6;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .slide-container {
            width: 1024px;
            height: 768px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .font-poppins {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        }
        .text-corporate-blue { color: #114a90; }
        .bg-corporate-blue { background-color: #114a90; }
        .text-corporate-red { color: #C0504D; }
        .bg-corporate-red { background-color: #C0504D; }
        .border-corporate-red { border-color: #C0504D; }
        .border-corporate-blue { border-color: #114a90; }
        .bg-light-gray { background-color: #F9FAFB; }
        .recommendation-card {
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        }
        .recommendation-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 8px 10px -6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .group:hover .group-hover\:bg-corporate-red { background-color: #C0504D; }
        .group:hover .group-hover\:bg-corporate-blue { background-color: #114a90; }
        .group:hover .group-hover\:text-white { color: #ffffff; }
        .group:hover .group-hover\:text-corporate-blue { color: #114a90; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="slide-container font-poppins">
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; width: 1024px; height: 8px; background-color: #C0504D; z-index: 1;"></div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; left: 48px; top: 32px; width: 800px; height: 80px; z-index: 10;">
<div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
<span class="w-8 h-1 bg-corporate-red"></span>
<p class="text-sm font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Estrategia</p>
</div>
<h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-corporate-blue">Mi recomendación</h2>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; right: 48px; top: 38px; width: 100px; height: 60px; z-index: 10; text-align: right;">
<p class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-200">19</p>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; right: 0; top: 80px; width: 256px; height: 256px; background-color: #F9FAFB; border-radius: 9999px; opacity: 0.5; z-index: 1;"></div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="shape" style="position: absolute; left: 40px; bottom: 40px; width: 128px; height: 128px; background-color: #eff6ff; border-radius: 9999px; opacity: 0.5; z-index: 1;"></div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; left: 48px; top: 130px; width: 768px; height: 80px; z-index: 10;">
<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 font-light leading-relaxed">
                Para negocios locales que inician, la eficiencia es clave. <span class="font-semibold text-corporate-blue">Empieza con Metricool gratis</span> para centralizar tu gestión sin costes iniciales.
            </p>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; left: 48px; top: 230px; width: 293px; height: 400px; z-index: 10;">
<div class="recommendation-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 relative overflow-hidden group h-full">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-20 h-20 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue text-3xl group-hover:bg-corporate-blue group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 mt-4">
<i class="fa-solid fa-share-nodes"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Cobertura Total</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">Cubre <span class="font-semibold">Instagram, Facebook y TikTok</span>. Gestiona tus principales canales desde un solo lugar.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; left: 365px; top: 230px; width: 293px; height: 400px; z-index: 10;">
<div class="recommendation-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 relative overflow-hidden group h-full">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-20 h-20 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue text-3xl group-hover:bg-corporate-blue group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 mt-4">
<i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Volumen Ideal</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600"><span class="font-semibold">20 posts/mes</span> son suficientes para empezar. Mantén la constancia sin saturarte.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div data-object="true" data-object-type="textbox" style="position: absolute; left: 682px; top: 230px; width: 293px; height: 400px; z-index: 10;">
<div class="recommendation-card bg-white border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-6 shadow-md flex flex-col items-center text-center gap-4 relative overflow-hidden group h-full">
<div class="absolute top-0 left-0 right-0 h-1 bg-gray-200 group-hover:bg-corporate-red transition-colors duration-300"></div>
<div class="w-20 h-20 flex-shrink-0 bg-blue-50 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-corporate-blue text-3xl group-hover:bg-corporate-blue group-hover:text-white transition-all duration-300 mt-4">
<i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group"></i>
</div>
<div class="flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center">
<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-2 group-hover:text-corporate-blue transition-colors">Escalable</h3>
<p class="text-gray-600">¿Necesitas más? Añade <span class="font-semibold">Meta Business Suite</span> (gratis) para complementar cuando crezcas.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>

    <div style="position: fixed; bottom: 20px; right: 20px; z-index: 9999; display: flex; gap: 10px; font-family: sans-serif; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">
        <a href="/slide-19" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Anterior</a>
        <span style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #fff; color: #333; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #ccc;">20 / 26</span>
        <a href="/slide-21" style="padding: 10px 15px; background: #114a90; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px; opacity: 1; pointer-events: auto">Siguiente</a>
    </div>
    
</body>
</html>


